name: Marvin E. CRUMP, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent at the State Correctional Institution at Graterford; District Attorney of the County of Philadelphia, Respondents

parties: Marvin E. CRUMP, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent at the State Correctional Institution at Graterford; District Attorney of the County of Philadelphia, Respondents.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 11th day of September, 2007, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is granted. The Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus Ad Subjicien-dum and Application for an Immediate Hearing are denied.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

casebody.head_matter:
Marvin E. CRUMP, Petitioner, v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Superintendent at the State Correctional Institution at Graterford; District Attorney of the County of Philadelphia, Respondents.
No. 113 EM 2007.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Sept. 11, 2007.
